[ProMED thanks Naomi Bryant for providing the links the Jamaican
Ministry of Health website. The announcements are not dated. There is
a discrepancy between the 194 cases cited above in the 2nd
announcement and the 43 cases cited from the RJR 94 Radio Jamaica
reported posted yesterday; the lower number cited yesterday is
probably more accurate, but this needs confirmation. - Mods.EP/MPP]
